svgedit编辑器

SVGEditSVG编辑

SVGEdit is a fast, web-based, JavaScript-driven SVG drawing editor that works in any modern browser. SVGEdit is based on a powerful SVG canvas @svgedit/svgcanvasSVGEdit 是一种基于 Web 的快速 JavaScript 驱动的 SVG 绘图编辑器，可在任何现代浏览器中运行。 SVGEdit 基于强大的 SVG 画布 @svgedit/svgcanvas

Contributions投稿

SVGEdit is the most popular open source SVG editor. It was started more than 13 years ago by a fantastic team of developers. Unfortunately, the product was not maintained for a quite long period. We decided to give this tool a new life by refreshing many aspects.SVGEdit 是最流行的开源 SVG 编辑器。它由一支出色的开发团队在 13 多年前创立。不幸的是，该产品没有维护很长时间。我们决定通过更新许多方面来赋予这个工具新的生命。

Please let us know with an issue or a discussions if you wish to contribute.如果您想做出贡献，请通过问题或讨论让我们知道。

I want to use SVGEdit我想使用 SVGEdit

Thanks to Netlify, you can access the following builds from your favorite browser:感谢 Netlify，您可以从您喜欢的浏览器访问以下版本：

  • Try SVGEdit V7 (master branch on github)尝试 SVGEdit V7（github 上的主分支）
  • Try SVGEdit V7 (latest published version on npm)尝试 SVGEdit V7（npm 上最新发布的版本）

Prior V7:之前的 V7：

We recommand using the V7 version but for older browsers or some abandoned features, you may need to access to old versions of SVGEdit.我们建议使用 V7 版本，但对于较旧的浏览器或一些废弃的功能，您可能需要访问旧版本的 SVGEdit。

  • Try SVGEdit 6.1.0 here在此处试用 SVGEdit 6.1.0
  • Try SVGEdit 5.1.0 here在此处试用 SVGEdit 5.1.0

Additional tip: you may try a version released on NPM using unpkg for example with version 3.2.0附加提示：您可以尝试使用 unpkg 在 NPM 上发布的版本，例如版本 3.2.0

  • https://unpkg.com/svgedit@3.2.0/editor/svg-editor.htmlhttps://unpkg.com/svgedit@3.2.0/editor/svg-editor.html

I want to host SVGEdit in my environment我想在我的环境中托管 SVGEdit

If you want to host a local version of SVGEdit, please follow these instructions:如果您想托管本地版本的 SVGEdit，请按照以下说明操作：

  1. Clone or copy the repository contents from github从 github 克隆或复制存储库内容
  2. run npm i to install dependencies运行 npm i 安装依赖项
  3. run npm run build --workspace @svgedit/svgcanvasto build the svgcanvas dependency locally运行 npm run build --workspace @svgedit/svgcanvas 以在本地构建 svgcanvas 依赖项
  4. to test, you can run npm run start to start a local server要测试，您可以运行 npm run start 来启动本地服务器
  5. and access http://localhost:8000/src/editor/index.html with a supported browser并使用支持的浏览器访问 http://localhost:8000/src/editor/index.html
  6. run npm run build to build a bundle that you can serve from your own web server.运行 npm run build 来构建一个可以从您自己的 Web 服务器提供服务的包。

I want to contribute to SVGEdit我想为 SVGEdit 做贡献

Thanks!谢谢！

SVG-Edit is made of two major components:SVG-Edit 由两个主要组件组成：

  1. The “svgcanvas” that takes care of the underlying svg edition. It can be used to build your own editor.负责底层 svg 版本的“svgcanvas”。它可用于构建您自己的编辑器。
  2. The “editor” that takes care of the editor UI (menus, buttons, etc.)负责编辑器 UI（菜单、按钮等）的“编辑器”

You should fork SVGEdit in your github environment and install locally SVGEdit as explained above. Before you submit your PR, please make sure you run locally:你应该在你的 github 环境中 fork SVGEdit，并按照上面的解释在本地安装 SVGEdit。在你提交你的 PR 之前，请确保你在本地运行：

  1. npm run lint to check that you follow the standardjs rules (https://standardjs.com/rules) for the linternpm 运行 lint 以检查您是否遵循 linter 的 standardjs 规则 (https://standardjs.com/rules)
  2. npm run test to run a suite of Cypress tests (https://www.cypress.io/).npm run test 运行一套 Cypress 测试 (https://www.cypress.io/)。

If you intend to contribute on a regular basis, let us know so we can add you in the maintainer team.如果您打算定期做出贡献，请告诉我们，以便我们将您加入维护团队。

I want to integrate SVGEdit into my own Web application我想将 SVGEdit 集成到我自己的 Web 应用程序中

V7 is changing significantly the way to integrate and customize SVG-Edit. You can have a look to index.html to see how you can insert a div element into your HTML code and inject the editor into the div.V7 正在显着改变集成和自定义 SVG-Edit 的方式。您可以查看 index.html 以了解如何将 div 元素插入 HTML 代码并将编辑器注入 div。

Warning: This div can be positionned anywhere in the DOM but it must have a numeric width and a numeric height (i.e. not ‘auto’ which happens when the div is hidden)警告：这个 div 可以定位在 DOM 中的任何位置，但它必须有一个数字宽度和一个数字高度（即不是“auto”，当 div 被隐藏时发生）

<head>
   <!-- You need to include the CSS for SVGEdit somewhere in your application -->
  <link href="./svgedit.css" rel="stylesheet" media="all"></link>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- svgedit container can be positionned anywhere in the DOM
       but it must have a width and a height -->
  <div id="container" style="width:100%;height:100vh"></div>
</body>
<script type="module">
  /* You need to call the Editor and load it in the <div> */
  import Editor from './Editor.js'
  /* for available options see the file `docs/tutorials/ConfigOptions.md` */
  const svgEditor = new Editor(document.getElementById('container'))
  /* initialize the Editor */
  svgEditor.init()
  /* set the configuration */
  svgEditor.setConfig({
          allowInitialUserOverride: true,
          extensions: [],
          noDefaultExtensions: false,
          userExtensions: []
  })
</script>
</html>

I want to build my own svg editor我想构建自己的 svg 编辑器

You can just use the underlying canvas and use it in your application with your favorite framework. See example in the demos folder or the svg-edit-react repository.您可以只使用底层画布，并在您的应用程序中使用您喜欢的框架。请参阅演示文件夹或 svg-edit-react 存储库中的示例。

To install the canvas:安装画布：

npm i -s '@svgedit/svgcanvas'npm i -s '@svgedit/svgcanvas'

you can then import it in your application:然后您可以将其导入您的应用程序：

import svgCanvas from '@svgedit/svgcanvas'从“@svgedit/svgcanvas”导入 svgCanvas

Supported browsers支持的浏览器

Developments and Continuous Integration are done with a Chrome environment. Chrome, FireFox and Safari recent versions are supported (in the meaning that we will try to fix bugs for these browsers).开发和持续集成是在 Chrome 环境中完成的。支持 Chrome、FireFox 和 Safari 最新版本（意味着我们将尝试修复这些浏览器的错误）。

Support for old browsers may require to use an older version of the package. However, please open an issue if you need support for a specific version of your browser so the project team can decide if we should support with the latest version.对旧浏览器的支持可能需要使用旧版本的包。但是，如果您需要支持特定版本的浏览器，请提出问题，以便项目团队决定我们是否应该支持最新版本。

Sample extension based on React基于 React 的示例扩展

A sample React component was used to build a svgedit extension. To activate:示例 React 组件用于构建 svgedit 扩展。激活：

  • “npm run build” from the extension folder “src/editor/react-extensions/react-test” in order to create the bundle for the extension.从扩展文件夹“src/editor/react-extensions/react-test”中“npm run build”，以便为扩展创建包。
  • modify “index.html” to activate the extension as a userExtensions修改“index.html”以将扩展激活为 userExtensions
svgEditor.setConfig({
          allowInitialUserOverride: true,
          extensions: [],
          noDefaultExtensions: false,
          userExtensions: ['./react-extensions/react-test/dist/react-test.js']
        })
